{"word":"G5235 - ὑπερβάλλω - hyperbállō - hoop-er-bal'-lo - Exceeding","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερβάλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperbállō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-bal'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Exceeding</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அதிகமாயிரு, மிகவும், மகா, வல்லவராயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to surpass in throwing; to throw over or beyond anything"},{"paragraph":"2. to transcend, surpass, exceed, excel"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G906 - βάλλω - bállō - bal'-lo/906\">G906</a>; to <i>throw beyond</i> the usual mark, that is, (figuratively) to <i>surpass</i> (only active participle <i>supereminent</i>): - exceeding, excel, pass.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5234/5234\">G5234</a>, <a href=\"#/G5235/5235\">G5235</a>, <a href=\"#/G5236/5236\">G5236</a>"}]}